OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTV cameras to film in      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcriminal courts for first  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftime in major law change   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, TV cameras will film in some criminal  
OL,6, courts in England and Wales for the    
OL,7, first time from Thursday.              
OL,9,FThe major change in the law will allow 
OL,10,Fbroadcasters to film judges sentencing 
OL,11,Fserious criminals.                     
OL,13,FThe arrival of cameras at the Old      
OL,14,FBailey and other Crown Courts comes    
OL,15,Fnine years after the move was first    
OL,16,Fpromised.                              
OL,18,FBroadcasting of entire trials will     
OL,19,Fremain off limits, unlike in the US and
OL,20,Fsome other nations.                    
